snippet.title: Photographer, Amber Smith - That's How You Feel? Podcast EP. 22
snippet.description:
THYFamily!

We had a very special guest join the show this week, none other than the BEST Central Valley photographer, Amber Smith. Amber came through with some GAME talking about how she was able to grow as a photographer, the importance of networking and social media, relationship advice, tips to beginner photographers, and much more! 

Be sure to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE!! Tell us how you feel one time!

If you're reading this far... PLEASE leave feedback on Apple Podcast. Give us a 5 star one time and let us know how you feel about the podcast! It would mean the SUN to us (see what I did there... no? whatever than).

Also, be sure to follow our Instagram, @thtshowyoufeel, for all the FIRE content including up to date new in sports and music, hilarious videos, see upcoming guests on the show, and much more!
